\end_layout

\end_inset

There's a vast difference between having a carload of miscellaneous facts sloshing around loose in your head and getting all mixed up in transit,
 and carrying the same assortment properly boxed and crated for convenient handling and immediate delivery.
\begin_inset ERT
status collapsed

\begin_layout Plain Layout

"-
\end_layout

\end_inset

Lorimer:
 Letters from a SelfMade Merchant to His Son at College.
\begin_inset Newline newline
\end_inset

 
\begin_inset ERT
