\end_layout

\end_inset

The power to grasp the essential features of problems is the great differentiation between the educated and the noneducated man.
 Undoubtedly the greatest advantage to be gained from a college education is the acquisition of a disciplined mind.
\begin_inset ERT
status collapsed

\begin_layout Plain Layout

