\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
As this chapter marks the completion of the first half of the course,
 it is felt that you should be given an opportunity to show how completely you have made the past seven parts of the chapters dealing with English a part of your regular equipment.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Some of the following sentences are correct,
 and others are incorrect,
 Read them over and in-
\begin_inset Newline newline
\end_inset

 stantly decide what changes need to be made in any of them.
 It may be a good thing for you to write them out.
