 Vice President of the L.
 A.
 D.
 Motors Corporation of Brooklyn,
 spoke to the employes of his organization on the subject of Loyalty and Coöperation.
 He closed his address with this ringing verse from Kipling's Second Jungle Book:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset ERT
