\end_layout

\end_inset

The public speaker must set forth with power and attractiveness the very same topic which others discuss in such tame and bloodless phraseology.
\begin_inset ERT
status collapsed

\begin_layout Plain Layout

"-
\end_layout

\end_inset

Cicero.
