\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
You and me must never be used as the subject of a sentence.
 For example:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
TO BE IMPRESSIVE AND CONVINCING 413
\begin_inset Newline newline
\end_inset

 Right:
