\end_inset

 This book will be as stimulating as a cold bath.
 It will tell you a lot about that most interesting of all subjects-yourself.
 It will reveal to you how much time you are wasting each day,
 how to stop the wastage,
 and how to utilize what you salvage.
 The entire book has only 103 pages.
 You can get through it easily in a week.
 Tear out twenty pages each morning,
 put them in your hip pocket.
 Then offer up upon the altar of the morning newspaper only ten minutes instead of the customary twenty or thirty minutes.
