Oh,
 dear,
 dear,
 dear,
 dear!
 How little that good,
 old man knew about war.
 If he had known anything about war,
 he ought to have known what any soldier in this audience knows is true,
 that it is next to a crime for andfficer of infantry ever in time of danger to 
\begin_inset Formula $g$
\end_inset

