status collapsed

\begin_layout Plain Layout

"
\end_layout

\end_inset

We live in deeds,
 not years;
 in feeling,
 not in figures on a dial;
 in thoughts,
 not breaths;
 we should count time by heart throbs,
 in the cause of right.
