\begin_layout Standard
By the Eternal!
 there is a man whose form should be cast in deathless bronze and the statue placed in every college of the land.
 It is not book learning young men need,
 or instruction about this and that,
 but a stiffening of the vertebræ which will cause them to be loyal to a trust,
 to act promptly,
\begin_inset Newline newline
\end_inset

